properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 10 at 2:55AM EST until January 12 at 3:00PM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...South to southwest winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30
kt and seas 5 to 10 feet expected.

* WHERE...The Atlantic coastal waters of New Jersey and Delaware.

* WHEN...From 6 AM Saturday to 3 PM EST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 6 AM SATURDAY TO 3 PM EST SUNDAY
